{"tid":882100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先聽到人講普教中","createTime":"2018-10-30T02:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T04:27:48.000Z","uid":81277,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5fbd3e02121a7ec1116b35814532d2aa6959e9b1","tid":882100,"uid":81277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:43:03.000Z","msg":"頭先喺西鐵站聽到個男人話<br />\n「香港實行普教中好吖其實」<br />\n然後佢隔離個女人問點解<br />\n<br />\n個男人話<br />\n「你唔見香港好多band 1中學都係英中咩<br />\n佢哋上堂除咗中文 都係用英文教<br />\n應該學普通話 用普通話教中文」<br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過 香港年輕一代<br />\n其實越黎越多都係大陸落黎嘅人<br />\n出到街聽到周圍着住校服好多都講普通話<br />\n以後都冇得唔普教中<br />\n其實好悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但亦正因為咁 我先更加覺得唔應該普教中<br />\n應該繼續用廣東話教書<br />\n先維護到廣東話呢個語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237c4ca30a71a42b275f6a44ce07644f940dd53a","tid":882100,"uid":175208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"即時同佢講 你返大陸啦"},{"pid":"99000802222c0cd923ae9e7212ec27f41faa88f3","tid":882100,"uid":81277,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"237c4ca30a71a42b275f6a44ce07644f940dd53a","tid":882100,"uid":175208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"即時同佢講 你返大陸啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:22:41.000Z","msg":"我本身都打算講 但係佢行得勁快<br />\n我又趕去整嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cc1237cfc9c472923f90a48b6d386ec09da4cd","tid":882100,"uid":838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"「你唔見香港好多band 1中學都係英中咩<br />\n佢哋上堂除咗中文 都係用英文教<br />\n應該學普通話 用普通話教中文」<br />\n<br />\nGoodest logic"},{"pid":"e2a1137bbb7d71af89c796cd171ef0c5bc5f40a7","tid":882100,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:55:52.000Z","msg":"普教英啦不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 